data.description: This stunning residence in the heart of West Rosamond is a must-see! Boasting a beautiful kitchen with a large island, it's perfect for meal prep or casual dining at the breakfast bar. With an open layout, the kitchen seamlessly flows into the spacious living room, ensuring you're always connected with loved ones while cooking. The living room offers ample space for large furniture and connects to a versatile formal dining room, adaptable to your needs as an office, playroom, or even an additional bedroom. The master bedroom is generously sized, accommodating large furniture comfortably, and features an ensuite bathroom with his and her sinks. Freshly painted just before hitting the market, this home exudes a fresh and inviting atmosphere. Enjoy the upgraded laminate flooring throughout. Parking is a breeze with the attached 3-car garage, a rare find not typically offered in new builds. Outside, the landscaped front and back yards provide a serene retreat. Don't miss out on this West Rosamond gem!
